    Black Aracnia smiled at Darkmouse, she was a tough little cookie to go 
through all of this. "Very good. Take your time. Also, if you like,  can have 
you placed in your quarters with a medical droid to watch over you."

    Paralysis looked at the virtual map and saw that several Allience members 
were assulting the skeleton of the once proud, but now shattered Ark. He 
slammed his fist down and cursed.
    Aerostreak, Gunatix, and Grappler sat on the bridge, learning a few 
things from Paralysis. They were as shocked as he was.
    "Black Aracnia! The Allience is attacking the Ark!"

    Aracnia stormed out of Darkmouses room without saying goodbye. Right now 
she had extreamly important matters to deal with. She ran down the corridor 
and into the bridge. She saw firsthand what was going on.
    "Well well, about time the Allience finally grows a backbone and dose 
something! Send a transmission to Darkone telling him that you, Aerostreak, 
Grappler, Adrax, and Autofire will be joining them. I will maintain things 
here and join you. Quickstrike will man the computers. Also, Atma, Decadel, 
and Hibichi..er..whatever, will join you as well. Hurry!" She ordered, 
looking to her crew.
